UniProt
## 📌 Purpose

UniProt is a protein knowledge database containing functional and structural information about proteins.

## 📌 Key Information Provided
Protein function
Domains
Subcellular location
Sequence length
Organism details
Protein families

## 📌 Common Uses
Protein annotation
Functional analysis
Conserved domain identification
Protein sequence retrieval

## 📌 File Types
FASTA
TXT
XML

## 📌 Important Sections
Function
Sequence
Domains
PTMs
Structure

